 | quote  ="My research team focuses on new classes of photoactive materials based on organometallics with new properties by combining components associating metal atoms and organic molecules that absorb or emit light."<ref name=spie.org>{{cite web|title=Vivian Wing-Wah Yam|url=http://spie.org/x87693.xml|publisher=[[SPIE]]|accessdate=8 March 2014}}</ref> 
